OL,5, A review into the BBC's migration      
OL,6, coverage has found while there is no   
OL,7, consistent bias towards one viewpoint, 
OL,8, there are risks to impartiality.       
OL,10,FCommissioned by the BBC board, in April
OL,11,F2023, Dr Madeline Sumption's review    
OL,12,Ffound while the BBC "produces a lot of 
OL,13,Fexcellent content on migration... there
OL,14,Fare also weaknesses".                  
OL,16,FThere were "risks to impartiality that 
OL,17,Fpoint in multiple directions".         
OL,19,FAnd it "often tells migration stories  
OL,20,Fthrough a narrow political lens".      
